First Department,

November, 1960

(November 1, 1960) (A) The People of the State of New York, Respondent, v. Lee Colligan, Appellant. (B) The People of the State of New York, Respondent, v. Roosevelt Joyner, Appellant. (C) The People of the State of New York, Respondent, v. Maud L. White, Appellant. (D) The People of the State of New York, Respondent, v. Donald White, Appellant, et al., Defendant.

[In each appeal] Judgment of conviction unanimously affirmed. No opinion. Concur — Botein, P. J., Breitel, Rabin, Yalente and Eager, JJ.
